short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Launch King County Library Catalog searches from Goodreads.com

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
goodKCLS provides users of goodreads.com a quick and easy way to search the King County Library System (KCLS) straight from goodreads.com. Whenever a user is looking at a book on goodreads an icon will appear in the address bar. Clicking on this icon will trigger the extension to search the KCLS catalog for the book, and open a new tab with the search results.

See website for release notes. A link for the goodKCLS website can be found in the details tab of this window.
